### Tenant Service
# Multi-tenant configuration and provisioning.
# Proto: api/proto/meridian/tenant/v1/tenant.proto
# Gateway: HTTP/JSON via Vanguard transcoding

## --- Tenant Management ---

### Create Tenant
POST {{host}}/v1/tenants
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenant_id}}

{
  "tenantId": "acme_energy",
  "displayName": "Acme Energy Corp",
  "settlementAsset": "GBP",
  "subdomain": "acme-energy"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("new_tenant_id", response.body.tenant.tenantId);
%}

### Retrieve Tenant
GET {{host}}/v1/tenants/{{new_tenant_id}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenant_id}}

### List Tenants
GET {{host}}/v1/tenants
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenant_id}}

### Update Tenant Status
PATCH {{host}}/v1/tenants/{{new_tenant_id}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenant_id}}

{
  "status": "TENANT_STATUS_ACTIVE"
}

### Get Provisioning Status
GET {{host}}/v1/tenants/{{new_tenant_id}}/provisioning-status
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenant_id}}

### Reconcile Migrations (specific tenant)
POST {{host}}/v1/tenants:reconcile-migrations
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenant_id}}

{
  "tenantId": "{{new_tenant_id}}"
}
